Wave Equation

∂2y(x,t)∂t2=c2∂2y(x,t)∂x2

7.4 μs

Finite Difference

yij+1−2yij+yij−1(Δt)2=c2yi+1j−2yij+yi−1j(Δx)2

Let α=(cΔtΔx)2 ;

yij+1=[αyi+1j+2(1−α)yij+αyi−1j]−yij−1

10.0 μs

Matrix form

y→j+1=M⋅y→j−y→j−1

M=(2(1−α)α0....α2(1−α)α0...0α2(1−α)α0..................0α2(1−α)α0...0α2(1−α)α....0α2(1−α))
